 "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 391344, "reply_to": 2000795, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 难道不是家里人觉得承受不起吗？", "timestamp": 1625583475, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2000927, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 391344, "reply_to": 2000795, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 老一辈大多有好几个孩子，医药费的分担很容易引起矛盾，而且如果有一家不愿意分担，很可能就没办法达成共识。如果家庭经济条件本就一般，估计去大医院更是难上加难", "timestamp": 1625583536, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2000974, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 391344, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "目前是必须挂着呼吸机才能活，转去大医院必须要用救护车转了，否则路上就会去世。估计是付不起从这样转的钱？", "timestamp": 1625583795, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001095, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 391344, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "具体是什么病？转去大城市搏一搏可以吗？", "timestamp": 1625584311, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001100, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 391344, "reply_to": 2000647, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 安乐死在中国不合法", "timestamp": 1625584323, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2001316, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 391344, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般放弃治疗都是治不起病的无奈之举... 节哀", "timestamp": 1625585385, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 391344, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "亲戚家的老人生病后上了差不多一个礼拜呼吸机，现在被县医院诊断认定为无法脱离呼吸机生存，家里决定拔掉呼吸机放弃治疗等死，洞友们怎么看这件事呢", "timestamp": 1625582369, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1625585385, "url": "", "vote": {}}}